# 🌐 Personal Portfolio Website

This is my personal **Portfolio Website**, built using **HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript**.  
It showcases my skills, services, projects, and ways to contact me. The website is fully responsive and optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.  

---

## 📌 Features

- **Responsive Design** – Works seamlessly on all screen sizes.
- **Hero Section** – Eye-catching introduction with bold text.
- **About Page** – Details about my background, skills, and professional journey.
- **Services Page** – A showcase of the services I provide, each with professional icons/images.
- **Projects Section** – Highlights of my best projects with links to live demos or GitHub repos.
- **Contact Page** – Contact form with JavaScript validation and direct links to my email & phone.
- **Footer** – Consistent footer across all pages with navigation & social links.
- **Interactivity** – Smooth navigation, form validation, and optional image sliders.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **HTML5** → Semantic structure for SEO and accessibility.  
- **CSS3** → Modern responsive design, Flexbox/Grid layout.  
- **JavaScript (ES6)** → Form validation, interactivity, and DOM manipulation.  
- **Netlify** → Hosting and deployment (free & fast).  

